  "title": "Furniture Wholesaler #79977",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Furniture Wholesaler</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: East – Ubi (Walking distance from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days / Mon-Fri: 9am-6pm, Sat: 9am-1pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD3500</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Research and identify new sales opportunities and customer needs in the furniture and interior renovation industry</li><li>Reach out to potential clients through cold calls, site visits, networking events, and social media platforms</li><li>Schedule and attend meetings with prospects to understand their project requirements and propose suitable solutions</li><li>Present and promote our furniture, renovation, and interior services effectively to clients</li><li>Prepare and follow up on quotations, proposals, and sales reports</li><li>Track sales performance, monitor financial data, and achieve monthly or quarterly sales targets</li><li>Ensure product and stock availability for client demonstrations or project requirements.</li><li>Represent the company at industry events, exhibitions, and trade shows to generate new leads</li><li>Negotiate pricing, terms, and contracts with clients to secure successful deals</li><li>Address customer feedback, manage complaints, and ensure client satisfaction</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams to ensure smooth project delivery</li><li>Gather market insights and competitor information to support sales strategies</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 1 year of experience in furniture, interior design or renovation industry</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79977 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
